    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Family firms are the engine room of the Scottish economy with around 300,000 family firms providing around 1 million jobs. The oldest family firm in Scotland is Auchtermuchty-based John White &amp; Sons which dates back to 1715, clearly demonstrating that family firms have the ability to last successfully for generations.</p>]]></Value>
